00:32.770 --> 00:34.400
Oppa!

00:38.400 --> 00:40.170
Hello.

00:40.170 --> 00:44.890
I'm Assistant Manager Lee Seung Yu's girlfriend, Lee Hye Ryeong.

00:56.900 --> 01:01.140
<i>Episode 13: The Best Love Affair</i>

01:02.560 --> 01:07.470
I had no idea Assistant Manager Lee had such a pretty girlfriend.

01:08.140 --> 01:11.440
