01:11.440 --> 01:13.540
That's true.

01:13.540 --> 01:17.350
Assistant Manager Lee doesn't really talk about his personal life.

01:17.350 --> 01:20.400
Assistant Manager Lee, you built some walls around yourself.

01:24.170 --> 01:28.840
So I guess you didn't know that Writer Seo Ji Won was his first love either.

01:34.210 --> 01:39.690
Oppa Seung Yu and Writer Seo were each others' first love.

01:39.690 --> 01:41.800
Isn't that funny?

01:46.080 --> 01:52.580
So the reason you wanted to be in charge of Writer Seo's 'Like a Watercolor'...

01:52.580 --> 01:55.080
No way. Wow.

01:55.080 --> 01:57.530
Hey, my oppa isn't that kind of person.

01:57.530 --> 02:00.200
He's a very objective person.

02:03.410 --> 02:07.900
It's been a long time since they've seen each other.

02:07.900 --> 02:09.840
Isn't that right, Writer Seo?

02:11.690 --> 02:14.850
It seems like those drama-like things can happen sometimes.

02:17.200 --> 02:21.880
It was just nice seeing you again Assistant Manager Lee, isn't that right?

02:23.270 --> 02:26.670
More so than nice, I was happy to see you.

02:27.640 --> 02:30.570
I really wanted to see you again.

02:38.490 --> 02:43.380
All of a sudden the atmosphere is somewhat...

02:45.680 --> 02:49.580
But why did you want to change the manager?

02:49.610 --> 02:51.480
You don't need to do that.

02:51.480 --> 02:54.790
Now that everyone knows, we can work comfortably.

02:54.790 --> 02:57.000
Isn't that right, Writer Seo?

03:07.520 --> 03:12.070
<i>[CAFE, Wine, Pasta, Coffee]</i>

03:12.070 --> 03:13.610
Ji Won.

03:16.210 --> 03:18.370
You still have something to say?

03:18.370 --> 03:19.470
Even after all this?

03:19.470 --> 03:23.640
- It's because she's still young. <br> - No, you're the one who's young.

03:23.640 --> 03:25.840
It's over so don't bother.

03:25.840 --> 03:27.020
Why are you being like this?

03:27.020 --> 03:29.810
I should be asking you that!

03:31.570 --> 03:36.180
Did you have fun putting me and Lee Hye Ryeong on your scale? Do I look easy?

03:36.180 --> 03:37.720
You know that's not true.

03:37.720 --> 03:42.270
I tried to understand you, but I can't.

03:45.070 --> 03:47.280
I thought of it too lightly.

03:58.840 --> 04:04.610
Please... just leave me out of your love games.

04:04.610 --> 04:11.060
Because I'm starting to hate myself for loving you for even a moment.

04:35.820 --> 04:37.430
Writer.

04:42.210 --> 04:45.670
Aren't you tired of being part of a third-rate drama?

04:47.950 --> 04:50.090
Do you want to do something fun with me?

05:21.010 --> 05:24.940
<i>So where do all the countless hours</i>

05:24.940 --> 05:27.710
<i>we spend together go?</i>

05:27.710 --> 05:32.830
Lee Ran Ju's World of Dreaming will be saying farewell to all of you.

05:36.550 --> 05:40.110
<i>The sadness that precedes our goodbye</i>

05:40.920 --> 05:43.230
<i>seem inevitable.</i>

05:46.530 --> 05:50.680
<i>But being separated with grief just hurts, right?</i>

05:56.100 --> 05:59.420
<i>To keep it a little tranquil,</i>

05:59.420 --> 06:02.800
<i>I would like to leave with a beautiful goodbye.</i>

06:03.630 --> 06:08.790
<i>Because the time we spent together was always blissful.</i>

06:10.230 --> 06:13.110
Was I ever happy?

06:16.410 --> 06:18.250
I can't remember.

06:37.710 --> 06:41.460
<i>Announcer Lee, your voice today was sexy.</i>

06:41.460 --> 06:44.920
<i>[Announcer Lee, your voice today was sexy~!!]</i>

06:46.250 --> 06:51.440
This has been Lee Ran Ju of Lee Ran Ju's World of Dreaming. Tomorrow—

06:56.770 --> 06:58.780
Have a good night.

07:24.780 --> 07:26.580
I'm here.

07:26.580 --> 07:28.240
You're here!

07:32.170 --> 07:36.550
Whose girlfriend is this pretty, lovable, and sexy?

07:36.550 --> 07:38.240
Hyeong Jun Yeong's.

07:38.940 --> 07:42.120
Hyeong Jun Yeong is one lucky guy.

07:42.120 --> 07:43.410
What did you make?

07:43.410 --> 07:45.250
Doenjang-jjigae. <i>(T/N: soybean paste stew)</i>

07:46.540 --> 07:48.210
Smell.

07:50.390 --> 07:52.020
Ta-da!

07:54.380 --> 07:56.050
Let's see.

08:01.580 --> 08:02.580
Is it good?

08:02.610 --> 08:04.410
- It's delicious. <br> - Really?

08:04.410 --> 08:08.110
That's a relief. It's not salty?

08:08.110 --> 08:09.370
It's really good.

08:09.370 --> 08:12.250
- This came out good. <br> - Hold on, hold on.

08:14.140 --> 08:19.310
♫ <i>You gently approach and blow into my heart</i> ♫

08:19.310 --> 08:21.210
Is it good?

08:21.210 --> 08:23.360
♫ <i>You're a happy breeze</i> ♫

08:23.360 --> 08:25.480
Slow down. Take your time.

08:27.460 --> 08:29.130
Cheers!

08:29.160 --> 08:31.680
Cheers!

08:51.600 --> 08:53.470
I thought we were doing something fun.

08:53.470 --> 08:56.100
You want to work again?

08:56.100 --> 08:58.750
Director, isn't this a bit harsh?

08:58.750 --> 09:02.810
Did you know you have an impatient personality?

09:02.810 --> 09:04.980
I said it's going to be fun.

09:15.270 --> 09:17.830
How do you like it? My publication space.

09:19.850 --> 09:21.660
Make yourself comfortable.

09:24.610 --> 09:25.990
Okay.

09:41.500 --> 09:43.000
How do you like it?

09:43.000 --> 09:45.310
It's fun.

09:48.220 --> 09:51.690
Oh. Is this...?

09:51.690 --> 09:53.520
That's right. It's my first movie.

09:53.520 --> 09:55.460
<i>You attend this academy as well?</i>

09:55.460 --> 09:58.620
<i>- Yes. <br> - It must be fate.</i>

09:59.850 --> 10:01.560
<i>Oh, that's right.</i>

10:02.500 --> 10:04.980
<i>I went home to look for a cable,</i>

10:04.980 --> 10:06.620
<i>but I didn't have one at home.</i>

10:06.620 --> 10:08.130
<i>- No, it's fine. <br> - No, take it.</i>

10:08.130 --> 10:10.430
<i>No. It's really okay.</i>

10:10.430 --> 10:13.220
<i>Then why don't just buy me coffee later?</i>

10:14.390 --> 10:16.870
<i>- Are you preparing to study abroad? <br> - Oh no, no, no.</i>

10:18.630 --> 10:22.030
<i>I was actually developing a photo app.</i>

10:22.030 --> 10:24.680
<i>A photo app?</i>

10:24.680 --> 10:26.300
<i>Yes.</i>

10:35.220 --> 10:40.490
<i>No matter where you are, I'll be there with you.</i>

10:41.360 --> 10:43.060
<i>And you?</i>

10:51.320 --> 10:53.600
<i>I love you.</i>

11:00.230 --> 11:01.770
<i>Goodbye.</i>

11:23.890 --> 11:30.350
<i>Timing and subtitles brought to you by <br> The How to Be Thirty Team @ Viki</i>

11:40.320 --> 11:41.730
