12:05.730 --> 12:08.330
I have no intention of breaking up with you.

12:09.190 --> 12:12.420
- Sorry. <br> - You're supposed to say you'll return to me.

12:18.100 --> 12:20.320
Writer Seo Ji Won...

12:22.560 --> 12:24.700
do you really love her?

12:27.160 --> 12:28.900
Just like you.

12:31.940 --> 12:34.580
I want to change her mind somehow.

12:51.360 --> 12:54.290
The movie was really great.

12:54.290 --> 12:57.190
Are you just being polite?

12:57.190 --> 12:59.950
You don't trust me that much?

13:01.500 --> 13:05.330
The movie did so badly that it doesn't seem deserved.

13:07.350 --> 13:10.670
It's a movie that touches the heart.

13:14.210 --> 13:16.270
The female star

13:16.270 --> 13:18.700
is your ex-girlfriend, isn't she?

13:20.330 --> 13:23.160
The movie can't hide it, can it?

13:23.160 --> 13:25.480
