13:28.330 --> 13:31.490
That's why I wanted to show you.

13:32.690 --> 13:37.340
I felt like I kept spying on your love life.

13:37.340 --> 13:39.970
I'm the type that can't be in debt.

13:41.270 --> 13:44.650
What I saw today was really huge.

13:44.650 --> 13:47.080
You know ratings for ridiculous dramas are unusually high.

13:47.080 --> 13:50.340
A noble art movie like that can't compare.

13:57.360 --> 14:01.850
Do you know the biggest difference between your 20s and 30s?

14:02.980 --> 14:05.670
I wonder. What could it be?

14:05.670 --> 14:07.300
Stamina?

14:08.250 --> 14:12.200
When love ends, you can immerse yourself in work.

14:15.240 --> 14:18.930
Let's just work from now on.

14:21.180 --> 14:22.770
Is this Cha Do Hoon's style of confort?

14:22.770 --> 14:26.470
Of course. You get it right away.

14:26.510 --> 14:30.670
♫ <i>You don't have to struggle, it's just going to flow</i> ♫

14:30.670 --> 14:34.660
Then, let's do our best.

14:37.840 --> 14:39.470
Okay.

14:42.990 --> 14:47.410
<i>That awful love finally ended.</i>

14:47.410 --> 14:49.710
<i>[Swiss Miss]</i>

15:03.380 --> 15:04.580
<i>[Swiss Miss]</i>

15:30.580 --> 15:32.870
<i>I had no lingering attachments.</i>

15:37.010 --> 15:40.940
<i>Writer Seo, I became your Assistant Manager again.</i>

15:40.940 --> 15:43.010
<i>Please take care of me.</i>

15:44.440 --> 15:47.340
<i>And I had no regrets.</i>

15:52.310 --> 15:55.380
<i>It just felt like a very long dream.</i>

15:58.810 --> 16:04.480
<i>A dream that fades away when you wake up in the morning.</i>

16:05.370 --> 16:09.020
