16:23.900 --> 16:25.400
- Boss Hong. <br> - Boss Hong.

16:25.480 --> 16:27.180
Give us some milk.

16:27.240 --> 16:30.410
<i>I was finding my everyday routines.</i>

16:30.410 --> 16:33.770
