18:53.060 --> 18:57.050
That's probably my facial hair. It's not like this is a latte.

18:57.050 --> 18:58.830
Hold on.

19:01.640 --> 19:02.780
Yes, Assistant Manager Yoon.

19:02.780 --> 19:04.840
Yeah, Wang PD. What?

19:04.840 --> 19:06.650
